PrecisReappointment of MARY ELIZABETH JAMIESON, of Ohsweken, Ontario, as a member of the National Aboriginal Economic Development Board; and designation of MARY ELIZABETH JAMIESON as Vice-Chairperson of that Board, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, effective January 23, 1998.
